msgctxt "sn20.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga "
msgstr "1. Similes "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Kulasutta "
msgstr "3. Families "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.264, sc1
msgctxt "sn20.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.3:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāni kānici kulāni bahutthikāni appapurisāni tāni suppadhaṃsiyāni honti corehi kumbhatthenakehi; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, those families with many women and few men are easy prey for bandits and thieves. "

msgctxt "sn20.3:1.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yassa kassaci bhikkhuno mettācetovimutti abhāvitā abahulīkatā so suppadhaṃsiyo hoti amanussehi. "
msgstr "In the same way any mendicant who has not developed and cultivated the heart’s release by love is easy prey for non-humans. "

msgctxt "sn20.3:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāni kānici kulāni appitthikāni bahupurisāni tāni duppadhaṃsiyāni honti corehi kumbhatthenakehi; "
msgstr "Those families with few women and many men are hard prey for bandits and thieves. "

msgctxt "sn20.3:1.5"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yassa kassaci bhikkhuno mettācetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā so duppadhaṃsiyo hoti amanussehi. "
msgstr "In the same way a mendicant who has developed and cultivated the heart’s release by love is hard prey for non-humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.3:1.6"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "sn20.3:1.7"
msgid "‘mettā no cetovimutti bhāvitā bhavissati bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will develop the heart’s release by love. We’ll cultivate it, make it our vehicle and our basis, keep it up, consolidate it, and properly implement it.’ "

msgctxt "sn20.3:1.8"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.3:1.9"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

